- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the proposed model uses machine learning techniques to improve entity linking. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as entity linking is a task in information retrieval and the paper proposes a new model to improve this task. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on evolutionary computing, but it does use neural networks to improve entity linking.
